97
00:06:17,920 --> 00:06:19,279
Lin Xiangyuan, awak memang hebat.

98
00:06:19,480 --> 00:06:21,160
Agak efisien juga.

99
00:06:21,640 --> 00:06:23,000
Apa yang Cik Jiang suruh,

100
00:06:23,200 --> 00:06:24,440
saya akan cuba sedaya upaya.

101
00:06:27,440 --> 00:06:28,440
Awak sudah tahu?

102
00:06:29,559 --> 00:06:30,399
Apa dia?

103
00:06:31,239 --> 00:06:33,160
Du Xiaosu sudah letak jawatan.

104
00:06:35,959 --> 00:06:36,600
Ya.

105
00:06:38,559 --> 00:06:40,359
Saya ingat dia hanya berpura-pura,

106
00:06:41,320 --> 00:06:43,000
tak sangka dia betul-betul pergi.

107
00:06:44,440 --> 00:06:45,679
Dia sanggup

108
00:06:46,079 --> 00:06:48,720
meninggalkan Syarikat Yu Tian,

109
00:06:49,679 --> 00:06:50,839
agak berani juga.

110
00:06:52,600 --> 00:06:54,200
Awak sebagai rakan sekelasnya,

111
