tak nak membantunya?

112
00:06:57,959 --> 00:07:00,000
Cik Jiang, jangan persenda saya.

113
00:07:00,399 --> 00:07:01,959
Sejak perjumpaan tahunan tempoh hari,

114
00:07:02,399 --> 00:07:03,679
kami langsung tak berhubung lagi.

115
00:07:03,720 --> 00:07:05,000
Kuat tekad awak.

116
00:07:05,799 --> 00:07:07,320
Dia sudah dewasa,

117
00:07:07,720 --> 00:07:09,000
tahu menjaga diri sendirinya.

118
00:07:09,079 --> 00:07:11,079
Entah bagaimana reaksi Abang Yuzheng

119
00:07:11,559 --> 00:07:13,000
