182
00:09:41,119 --> 00:09:42,960
Agak baik, dia berada.

183
00:09:43,039 --> 00:09:44,159
Kacak dan kaya,

184
00:09:44,280 --> 00:09:45,520
dia juga berkebolehan.

185
00:09:46,520 --> 00:09:47,400
