203
00:10:30,440 --> 00:10:31,960
berbanding dengan mi segera ini.

204
00:10:33,479 --> 00:10:34,080
Jumpa lagi.

205
00:10:35,239 --> 00:10:36,440
Jumpa lagi.

206
00:10:36,479 --> 00:10:38,640
